"><figure class="media-object-image img-header"><div class="image-container responsive-media"><img width="700" height="431" src="https://images.wsj.net/im-828171?width=700&amp;height=431" alt="" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></div><figcaption class="imageCaption"></figcaption></figure></div></div></div><div class="articleBody" data-sbid="WP-WSJO-0000022870"><div class="clearfix bylineWrap"><div class="byline">华尔街日报图书工作人员</div><time class="timestamp article__timestamp flexbox__flex--1">美国东部时间 2023 年 8 月 4 日下午 2:09 </time></div><div subscriptions-actions="" subscriptions-display="NOT data.noSharing"><div class="share-bar"><amp-social-share type="system" width="72" height="24" data-param-url="https://www.wsj.com/articles/14-books-we-read-this-week-ec01d24e"></amp-social-share></div></div><section subscriptions-section="content"><h3> <a href="https://www.wsj.com/articles/the-good-virus-review-an-unlikely-healer-1eb05588?mod=article_inline" target="_blank" class="icon none">《好病毒》评论：一个不可能的治愈者</a></h3><div class="media-object scope-
