"><div class="media-object-interactiveLink"><div class="image-container"> <a class="interactive-link" href="https://www.wsj.com/articles/the-good-virus-review-an-unlikely-healer-1eb05588"><img width="16" height="10" src="https://images.wsj.net/im-829253?width=700&amp;height=465" alt="不明确的" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><span class="image-interactive-icon">
            </span></a></div><div class="wsj-article-caption"><span class="wsj-article-credit">博尔兹沃伊/阿拉米</span></div></div></div><p>噬菌体疗法在细菌上释放病毒。这种治疗可能会挽救生命。<em>大卫·A·谢维茨 (David A. Shaywitz) 评论</em></p><p><a href="https://www.wsj.com/articles/the-good-virus-review-an-unlikely-healer-1eb05588?mod=article_inline" target="_blank" class="icon none">阅读评论</a></p><div class="media-object scope-web|mobileapps
          smallrule
"><div class="wsj-article-page-rule"></div></div><h3> <a href="https://www.wsj.com/articles/three-books-on-the-second-amendment-a2c669e8?mod=article_inline" target="_blank" class="icon none">关于第二修正案的三本书</a></h3><div class="media-object scope-
          inline
"><div class="media-object-interactiveLink"><div class="image-container"> <a class="interactive-link" href="https://www.wsj.com/articles/three-books-on-the-second-amendment-a2c669e8"><img width="16" height="10" src="https://images.wsj.net/im-829792?width=700&amp;height=510" alt="不明确的" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><span class="image-interactive-icon">
            </span></a></div><div class="wsj-article-caption"><span class="wsj-article-credit">斯科特·奥尔森/盖蒂图片社</span></div></div></div><p>一位小说家、一位教授和一位法律学者最近写的书可能会给美国关于枪支的古老争论注入新的见解——也可能不会。<em>巴顿·斯威姆的评论</em></p><p><a href="https://www.wsj.com/articles/three-books-on-the-second-amendment-a2c669e8?mod=article_inline" target="_blank" class="icon none">阅读评论</a></p><div class="media-object scope-web|mobileapps
